  "notes": "Interior cave (15x9 blocks, 30x18 tiles) connecting Route 27's two warp points. Confirmed size: TohjoFalls.blk = 135 bytes = 15x9 blocks. Requires Surf to enter the central pool. A Waterfall is present inside (HM07 required to ascend). The Moon Stone sits in the western alcove (event flag EVENT_TOHJO_FALLS_MOON_STONE). Wild encounters include Zubat, Golbat, Rattata, Raticate, and Slowpoke. The sign outside on Route 27 reads: 'TOHJO FALLS - THE LINK BETWEEN KANTO AND JOHTO'. No trainers inside. The cave serves as the sole HM-gated passage between Johto and Kanto regions."
